/.premium/impressive-idf-rescue-op-proves-that-netanyahu-can-take-responsibility-when-he-wants-to/0000018d-9ee3-d747-a78f-fefbcdd90000</link><description>在加沙地带南部的拉法，两名以色列人质被完美解救，这一切都归功于士兵和他们的指挥官。任何声称将以同样大胆的方式释放所有剩余人质的人都是在撒谎。这并非巧合，因为他们正是试图让我们相信没有机会达成另一项协议的人</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 00:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/impressive-idf-rescue-op-proves-that-netanyahu-can-take-responsibility-when-he-wants-to/0000018d-9ee3-d747-a78f-fefbcdd90000</guid></item><item><title>英国工党与一名候选人断绝关系，该候选人称以色列允许哈马斯发动袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/british-labour-party-cuts-ties-with-candidate-who-said-israel-allowed-oct-7-to-happen/0000018d-9f93-df62-a3fd-9f9f563c0001</link><description>爱资哈尔·阿里已为这些言论道歉，但被他的政党停职——该党仍在从前党魁杰里米·科尔宾领导下的制度性反犹太主义指控中恢复过来</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 00:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/british-labour-party-cuts-ties-with-candidate-who-said-israel-allowed-oct-7-to-happen/0000018d-9f93-df62-a3fd-9f9f563c0001</guid></item><item><title>被解雇的以色列国防军军官被指控在战争期间冒充现役情报官员分享机密信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/discharged-idf-officer-accused-of-posing-as-active-intel-officer-during-war/0000018d-9eb1-d92c-a9ed-fff973460000</link><description>被告参加了敏感的简报会，被指控犯有严重欺诈、移交机密信息、无意破坏国家安全的间谍活动以及未经授权进入军事场所等罪名。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/.premium/discharged-idf-officer-accused-of-posing-as-active-intel-officer-during-war/0000018d-9eb1-d92c-a9ed-fff973460000</guid></item><item><title>美国反对以色列在没有为流离失所的加沙人制定计划的情况下袭击拉法；欧盟首席外交官敦促削减援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-12/ty-article/u-s-opposes-rafah-raid-without-plan-for-displaced-gazans-eu-chief-diplomat-urges-aid-cut/0000018d-9ef4-d747-a78f